{"word":"G2105 - εὐδία - eudía - yoo-dee'-ah - Fair weather","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εὐδία</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">eudía</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">yoo-dee'-ah</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Fair weather</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"செவ்வானம் - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"a serene sky, fair weather"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Feminine from <a href=\"#/G2095 - εὖ - eû - yoo/2095\">G2095</a> and the alternate of <a href=\"#/G2203 - Ζεύς - Zeús - dzyooce/2203\">G2203</a> (as the god of the weather); a <i>clear sky</i>, that is, <i>fine weather:</i> - fair weather.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}